---
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Trainings">
  <div
    class="bg-[url('/eng-hero.png')] grid bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat bg-origin-border px-6 md:px-12 md:py-14 py-24 md:place-content-center md:place-items-start md:min-h-[300px]">
  </div>
  <Container>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl text-gray-800">
        Free Engineering Training
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        In partnership with Rucotech, Olu of Warri Palace Liaison Authority
        (owpla.org) is organizing a two-weeks free upskill training for
        Engineering and Natural Science graduates. See the details below, if you
        meet the criteria, click the “Register now” button to apply.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        Graduates with a minimum qualification of Higher National Diploma (HND)
        and currently yet to be employed in the fields of;<br />
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6">
          <li>Mechanical Engineering</li>
          <li>Petroleum Engineering</li>
          <li>Chemical Engineering</li>
          <li>Civil Engineering</li>
          <li>Production Engineering</li>
          <li>Geology</li>
          <li>Chemistry/Industrial Chemistry</li>
          <li>Physics, etc</li>
        </ol>
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        After form submission a selection process will be done to ensure only
        qualified and serious minded candidates are provided with this
        opportunity. If you are selected, you will receive a mail with a unique
        QR code, this will grant you access to the training venue.<br />
        There is limited spots for this training, we will not accept more applications
        once the spots have been filled.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        Training will be held between 10th - 22nd of July, 2024. Registration
        closed midnight, November 30, 2023.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://forms.gle/zbCuMe1CFVNSMMGU7"
        class="flex gap-1 max-w-fit items-center justify-start bg-white text-[#2947A9] font-bold"
        rel="noopener">
        Register now
      </a>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
